title: The Maltese Falcon (Unabridged)
description:
Audio Books : Mystery : MP3/128Kbps : English


Written by Dashiell Hammett. The novel that began the private eye genre. 

It's 1921 and Sam Spade, a private eye, is looking for the person or persons who killed his partner when he stumbles upon a group of strange people all after a statuette that was stolen from the Spanish monarchy centuries earlier. 

Read by William Dufris. 

One file, about 7 hours long. 


Enjoy and Seed!!
